{"title":"Hexo的前置准备","uid":"f0c1ca3b0c9f9793ae5dde4fc58c7e46","slug":"Hexo个人博客搭建1","date":"2022-08-05T10:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-08-18T17:35:07.001Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo个人博客搭建1.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/noh/04175.jpg","content":"<p>Before use the Hexo to write down our articles , it was easy to see that something should be configured by ourselves.</p>\n<p>link:</p>\n<p>Hexo安装教程<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty</a></p>\n<p>Aurora主题更换教程<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1hU4y1o7w3\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1hU4y1o7w3</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"一、-安装node-js\"><a href=\"#一、-安装node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、 安装node.js\"></a>一、 安装node.js</h2><p>前往node.js官网<a href=\"https://node.js.org/\">https://node.js.org</a></p>\n<p>下载最新版本的安装包（<em>windows&#x2F;linux</em>）。选好解压位置，即可无脑下一步。</p>\n<p>打开cmd（管理员模式）输入以下代码查看 <em><strong>node</strong></em> 与 <em><strong>npm</strong></em> 版本，确认与所下版本一致。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">node -v</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm -v</code></pre>\n\n<p>对<em>npm</em>换源以加快下载速度，选用淘宝的国内镜像：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install -g cnpm --registry&#x3D;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre>\n\n<p>查看<em>cnpm</em>下载情况</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cnpm -v</code></pre>\n\n<p>等待下载完成，以后就可以直接使用<strong>cnpm</strong>进行包的安装。</p>\n<h2 id=\"二、-安装Git\"><a href=\"#二、-安装Git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、 安装Git\"></a>二、 安装Git</h2><p>Git官网<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/\">https://git-scm.com/</a></p>\n<p>安装指南：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A/article/details/122704934\">https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A/article/details/122704934</a></p>\n<p>安装视频(07)：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vy4y1s7k6\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vy4y1s7k6</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"下面是个人安装历程\"><a href=\"#下面是个人安装历程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下面是个人安装历程\"></a><em><strong>下面是个人安装历程</strong></em></h3><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>点击查看更多</summary>\n<p><p>1.官网下载安装包并解压（速度过慢建议使用迅雷下载）</p>\n<p>2.组件全✔</p>\n<p>3.<em><strong>Git命令使用，选择Git bash加终端cmd</strong></em></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/photo/Git1.png\" alt=\"sample1 截图1\" title=\"示例1\"></p>\n<p>4.其余一路默认，直到安装结束</p>\n<p>5.验证<em>Git</em> 安装成功</p>\n<p>选择加入<em>Git</em>仓库的文件夹右键选择 <em><strong>Git Bash Here</strong></em></p>\n<p>输入如下命令，查看Git版本确认安装成功：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Git --version</code></pre>\n\n<p>ps：<em>未完待续，将来会更新Git&#x2F;Github专题</em></p>\n</p>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"三、-安装Hexo并配置\"><a href=\"#三、-安装Hexo并配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、 安装Hexo并配置\"></a>三、 安装Hexo并配置</h2><p>输入安装命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cnpm install -g hexo-cil</code></pre>\n\n<p>验证：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo -v</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"/img/photo/Hexo1.png\" alt=\"验证\" title=\"hexo验证\"></p>\n<p>新建一个存放 <em><strong>Blog</strong></em> 的文件夹,在 <em><strong>cmd</strong></em> 中使用 <em><strong>cd命令</strong></em> 进入该文件夹，然后：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo init\n&#x2F;&#x2F;出现 start blogging with hexo! 即安装完成</code></pre>\n\n<p>hexo会自动clone生成博客，生成完成后我们的<em>blog</em>就算初步成功了</p>\n<h2 id=\"四、-安装Aurora，配置主题\"><a href=\"#四、-安装Aurora，配置主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、 安装Aurora，配置主题\"></a>四、 安装Aurora，配置主题</h2><p>1.在控制台中，进入 Hexo 项目的根目录，然后运行以下命令安装主题:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install hexo-theme-aurora --save</code></pre>\n\n<p>2.创建一个配置文件。你只需要在 Hexo 博客的根目录下创建一个 _config.aurora.yml 配置文件来配置主题。</p>\n<p>找到：<em><strong>你的博客所在的根目录\\node_modules\\hexo-theme-aurora\\ _config.yml</strong></em> ，并将 <em><strong>_config.yml</strong></em>，复制到博客所在根目录重命名为 <em><strong>_config.aurora.yml</strong></em></p>\n<p>3.设置 <em><strong>permalink</strong></em></p>\n<p>只需打开<strong>Hexo</strong>根目录下的**_config.yml** ,修改 <em><strong>permalink</strong></em> 参数为 <strong>&#x2F;post&#x2F;:title.html</strong> ，如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"># URL\n## Set your site url here. For example, if you use GitHub Page, set url as &#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;username.github.io&#x2F;project&#39;\nurl: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;tridiamond.tech\npermalink: &#x2F;post&#x2F;:title.html\npermalink_defaults:\npretty_urls:\n  trailing_index: true # Set to false to remove trailing &#39;index.html&#39; from permalinks\n  trailing_html: true # Set to false to remove trailing &#39;.html&#39; from permalinks</code></pre>\n\n<p>4.设置代码高亮</p>\n<p>最后主题是使用 <em><strong>Prismjs</strong></em> 来实现代码高亮显示，但 <em><strong>Hexo</strong></em> 默认是使用 <em><strong>highlightjs</strong></em>，因此你需要更改 <em><strong>Hexo</strong></em> 配置来使用 <em><strong>Prismjs</strong></em>:</p>\n<p>我们需要：</p>\n<p>把 <em><strong>highlight</strong></em> 的启用改为 <em><strong>false</strong></em></p>\n<p>把 <em><strong>prismjs</strong></em> 的启用改为 <em><strong>true</strong></em></p>\n<p>把 <em><strong>prismjs</strong></em> 下的 <em><strong>preprocess</strong></em> 改为 <em><strong>false</strong></em></p>\n<p>如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">highlight:\n  enable: false\n  line_number: true\n  auto_detect: false\n  tab_replace: &#39;&#39;\n  wrap: true\n  hljs: false\nprismjs:\n  enable: true\n  preprocess: true\n  line_number: true\n  tab_replace: &#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>6.创建 “关于 (<br><em><strong>about</strong></em><br>)” 页面</p>\n<p>主题默认开启了 about 页面，所以我们需要创建这个 about 页，要不主题就无法正常显示 about 页。</p>\n<p>我们需要进入 <em><strong>source</strong></em> 文件夹下，新建一个 <em><strong>about</strong></em> 文件夹，在 <em><strong>about</strong></em> 中，右键新建一个 <em><strong>txt文件</strong></em> 重命名为 <em><strong>index.md</strong></em> 即可</p>\n<p>现在，你可以随意修改这个 index.md markdown 文件中的内容，此文件的内容将会现在在我们的 about 页面中。</p>\n<p>7.重新生成与本地服务器</p>\n<p><em><strong>命令行（cmd）</strong></em>中使用以下命令来运行本地环境。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo clean\nhexo g\nhexo s</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>改变了任何配置都需要重新生成 Hexo 的静态文件！</p>\n\n</div>\n<p>当文件都生成完毕之后，就可以通过 <em><strong><a href=\"https://localhost:4000/\">https://localhost:4000</a></strong></em> 访问你的博客了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"五、-Github配置-x2F-初次上传网页\"><a href=\"#五、-Github配置-x2F-初次上传网页\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、 Github配置&#x2F;初次上传网页\"></a>五、 Github配置&#x2F;初次上传网页</h2><p>下拉仓库代码 <em><strong>Git Bash Here</strong></em> ：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git clone Http(Github仓库地址http)</code></pre>\n\n<p>未完待续</p>\n<p>We mix the Github Pages and Hexo that is uisng the Aurora , which is a themes with powerful fuctions , to make up our personal Blog .</p>\n<p>Hexo博客官方文档：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/\">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></p>\n<p>Aurora主题官方文档：<a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/\">https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Before use the Hexo to write down our articles , it was easy to see that something should be configured by ourselves. link: Hexo安装教程https://...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.9k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Blog.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Blog.json"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85node-js\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、 安装node.js</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Git\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二、 安装Git</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8E%86%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">下面是个人安装历程</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Hexo%E5%B9%B6%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">三、 安装Hexo并配置</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Aurora%EF%BC%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">四、 安装Aurora，配置主题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%94%E3%80%81-Github%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-x2F-%E5%88%9D%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">五、 Github配置&#x2F;初次上传网页</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"肇蘩","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/1.jpg","link":"/","description":"前进，向前进！落后就会灭亡！","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Hello Hexo","uid":"bfdf9a8b10194568dc6bf593b1470633","slug":"hello-world","date":"2022-08-05T10:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-08-18T17:35:09.558Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/noh/Gtr.jpg","text":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":626,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Blog.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Blog.json"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"author":{"name":"肇蘩","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/1.jpg","link":"/","description":"前进，向前进！落后就会灭亡！","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{}}